org.apache.streams.config

Class StreamsConfigurator<T extends StreamsConfiguration>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.streams.config.StreamsConfigurator<T>

  • public class StreamsConfigurator<T extends StreamsConfiguration>
extends Object
    StreamsConfigurator supplies the entire typesafe tree to runtimes and modules. StreamsConfigurator also supplies StreamsConfiguration POJO to runtimes and modules.
